All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AllEventRequest
Stores the data of an HTTP request for a request for every event for a given user.
AllEventResult
Stores the data for an HTTP result with all the event data for the user.
AllPersonRequest
Stores the data of an HTTP request for a request for every Person related to a given user.
AllPersonResult
Stores the data for an HTTP result with all the Person data for the user.
AuthToken
Authentication token of a user.
AuthTokenDao
Provides access to authentication token related queries to the SQLite database.
ClearLoadDAO
Provides access to database-wide queries such as clearing and loading
ClearRequest
A (blank) object representing an HTTP request to clear the database
ClearResult
Stores the data for an HTTP result with all the information of the outcome of clearing the database.
ClearService
Handles the clearing of the database
Event
Event of a person Object for a user.
EventDao
Provides access to Event-object related queries to the SQLite database.
EventRequest
Stores the data of an HTTP request for a request for a single event for a given user's family.
EventResult
Stores the data for an HTTP result with all the event data for the requested single event.
EventService
Handles the retrieval of event objects for the Handler classes
FillRequest
Stores the data for an HTTP request to make the family tree of a given user
FillResult
Data for an HTTP response as for how the filing of a user's tree went
FillService
Handles the Filling of data given a FilLRequest
HelloWorld
 
InvalidAuthTokenException
Thrown if the authentication token given is missing/invalid for the given request
InvalidInputException
Thrown if the given parameters are missing/incorrect
LoadRequest
Stores data for an HTTP request to load data
LoadResult
Stores the data for an HTTP request that goes back to the user after a Load request
LoadService
Handles the loading of data given a LoadRequest
LoginRequest
Stores the data for an HTTP request to login
LoginResult
Stores the data for an HTTP request for the result of a login request
LoginService
Handles the login of a user given a LoginRequest
Person
Person Object for a family member of a user.
PersonDao
Provides access to Person-object related queries to the SQLite database.
PersonRequest
Stores the data for an HTTP request to get the information on a person object
PersonResult
Stores the data for an HTTP result for information on a specific Person object
PersonService
Handles the retrieval of Person objects for the Handler classes
RegisterRequest
Stores the data for an HTTP request to register a new user
RegisterResult
Data for an HTTP result that tells whether a register attempt was successful
RegisterService
Handles the registration of a user given a RegisterRequest
Server
 
User
User Object for a user of the FamilyMap service.
UserDao
Provides access to user related queries to the database, such as retrieving and creating users
UsernameTakenException
Thrown if given username for registering is already taken
